33FlowScene::FlowScene(std::shared_ptr<DataModelRegistry> registry, QObject *parent) : QGraphicsScene(parent), _registry(std::move(registry))
34{
35 setItemIndexMethod(QGraphicsScene::NoIndex);
36 // This connection should come first
37 connect(this, &FlowScene::connectionCreated, this, &FlowScene::setupConnectionSignals);
38 connect(this, &FlowScene::connectionCreated, this, &FlowScene::sendConnectionCreatedToNodes);
39 connect(this, &FlowScene::connectionDeleted, this, &FlowScene::sendConnectionDeletedToNodes);
40 connect(this, &FlowScene::nodeContextMenu, this, &FlowScene::sceneContextMenuEvent);
41}
42FlowScene::FlowScene(QObject *parent) : FlowScene(std::make_shared<DataModelRegistry>(), parent)
43{
44}

49//------------------------------------------------------------------------------
50std::shared_ptr<Connection> FlowScene::createConnection(PortType connectedPort, Node &node, PortIndex portIndex)
51{
52 auto connection = std::make_shared<Connection>(connectedPort, node, portIndex);
53 auto cgo = detail::make_unique<ConnectionGraphicsObject>(*this, *connection);
54 // after this function connection points are set to node port
55 connection->setGraphicsObject(std::move(cgo));
56 _connections[connection->id()] = connection;
57 // Note: this connection isn't truly created yet. It's only partially created.
58 // Thus, don't send the connectionCreated(...) signal.
59 connect(connection.get(), &Connection::connectionCompleted, this, [this](Connection const &c) { connectionCreated(c); });
60 return connection;
61}
62std::shared_ptr<Connection> FlowScene::createConnection(Node &nodeIn, PortIndex portIndexIn, Node &nodeOut, PortIndex portIndexOut,
63 TypeConverter const &converter)
64{
65 auto connection = std::make_shared<Connection>(nodeIn, portIndexIn, nodeOut, portIndexOut, converter);
66 auto cgo = detail::make_unique<ConnectionGraphicsObject>(*this, *connection);
67 nodeIn.nodeState().setConnection(PortType::In, portIndexIn, *connection);
68 nodeOut.nodeState().setConnection(PortType::Out, portIndexOut, *connection);
69 // after this function connection points are set to node port
70 connection->setGraphicsObject(std::move(cgo));
71 // trigger data propagation
72 nodeOut.onDataUpdated(portIndexOut);
73 _connections[connection->id()] = connection;
74 connectionCreated(*connection);
75 return connection;
76}
77std::shared_ptr<Connection> FlowScene::restoreConnection(QJsonObject const &connectionJson)
78{
79 QUuid nodeInId = QUuid(connectionJson["in_id"].toString());
80 QUuid nodeOutId = QUuid(connectionJson["out_id"].toString());
81 PortIndex portIndexIn = connectionJson["in_index"].toInt();
82 PortIndex portIndexOut = connectionJson["out_index"].toInt();
83 auto nodeIn = _nodes[nodeInId].get();
84 auto nodeOut = _nodes[nodeOutId].get();
85 auto getConverter = [&]() {
86 QJsonValue converterVal = connectionJson["converter"];
87 if (!converterVal.isUndefined())
88 {
89 QJsonObject converterJson = converterVal.toObject();
90 NodeDataType inType{ converterJson["in"].toObject()["id"].toString(), converterJson["in"].toObject()["name"].toString() };
91 NodeDataType outType{ converterJson["out"].toObject()["id"].toString(), converterJson["out"].toObject()["name"].toString() };
92 auto converter = registry().getTypeConverter(outType.id(), inType.id());
93 if (converter)
94 return converter;
95 }
96 return TypeConverter{};
97 };
98 std::shared_ptr<Connection> connection = createConnection(*nodeIn, portIndexIn, *nodeOut, portIndexOut, getConverter());
99 // Note: the connectionCreated(...) signal has already been sent
100 // by createConnection(...)
101 return connection;
102}
103void FlowScene::deleteConnection(const Connection &connection)
104{
105 auto it = _connections.find(connection.id());
106 if (it != _connections.end())
107 {
108 connection.removeFromNodes();
109 _connections.erase(it);
110 }
111}
112Node &FlowScene::createNode(std::unique_ptr<NodeDataModel> &&dataModel)
113{
114 auto node = detail::make_unique<Node>(std::move(dataModel));
115 auto ngo = detail::make_unique<NodeGraphicsObject>(*this, *node);
116 node->setGraphicsObject(std::move(ngo));
117 auto nodePtr = node.get();
118 _nodes[node->id()] = std::move(node);
119 nodeCreated(*nodePtr);
120 return *nodePtr;
121}
122Node &FlowScene::restoreNode(QJsonObject const &nodeJson)
123{
124 QString modelName = nodeJson["model"].toObject()["name"].toString();
125 auto dataModel = registry().create(modelName);
126 if (!dataModel)
127 throw std::logic_error(std::string("No registered model with name ") + modelName.toLocal8Bit().data());
128 auto node = detail::make_unique<Node>(std::move(dataModel));
129 auto ngo = detail::make_unique<NodeGraphicsObject>(*this, *node);
130 node->setGraphicsObject(std::move(ngo));
131 node->restore(nodeJson);
132 auto nodePtr = node.get();
133 _nodes[node->id()] = std::move(node);
134 nodePlaced(*nodePtr);
135 nodeCreated(*nodePtr);
136 return *nodePtr;
137}
138void FlowScene::removeNode(Node &node)
139{
140 // call signal
141 nodeDeleted(node);
142 for (auto portType : { PortType::In, PortType::Out })
143 {
144 auto nodeState = node.nodeState();
145 auto const &nodeEntries = nodeState.getEntries(portType);
146 for (auto &connections : nodeEntries)
147 {
148 for (auto const &pair : connections) deleteConnection(*pair.second);
149 }
150 }
151 _nodes.erase(node.id());
152}

161void FlowScene::iterateOverNodes(std::function<void(Node *)> const &visitor)
162{
163 for (const auto &_node : _nodes)
164 {
165 visitor(_node.second.get());
166 }

168void FlowScene::iterateOverNodeData(std::function<void(NodeDataModel *)> const &visitor)
169{
170 for (const auto &_node : _nodes)
171 {
172 visitor(_node.second->nodeDataModel());
173 }
174}
175void FlowScene::iterateOverNodeDataDependentOrder(std::function<void(NodeDataModel *)> const &visitor)
176{
177 std::set<QUuid> visitedNodesSet;
178 // A leaf node is a node with no input ports, or all possible input ports
179 // empty
180 auto isNodeLeaf = [](Node const &node, NodeDataModel const &model) {
181 for (unsigned int i = 0; i < model.nPorts(PortType::In); ++i)
182 {
183 auto connections = node.nodeState().connections(PortType::In, i);
184 if (!connections.empty())
185 {
186 return false;
187 }
188 }
189 return true;
190 };
191 // Iterate over "leaf" nodes
192 for (auto const &_node : _nodes)
193 {
194 auto const &node = _node.second;
195 auto model = node->nodeDataModel();
196 if (isNodeLeaf(*node, *model))
197 {
198 visitor(model);
199 visitedNodesSet.insert(node->id());
200 }
201 }
202 auto areNodeInputsVisitedBefore = [&](Node const &node, NodeDataModel const &model) {
203 for (size_t i = 0; i < model.nPorts(PortType::In); ++i)
204 {
205 auto connections = node.nodeState().connections(PortType::In, i);
206 for (auto &conn : connections)
207 {
208 if (visitedNodesSet.find(conn.second->getNode(PortType::Out)->id()) == visitedNodesSet.end())
209 {
210 return false;
211 }
212 }
213 }
214 return true;
215 };
216 // Iterate over dependent nodes
217 while (_nodes.size() != visitedNodesSet.size())
218 {
219 for (auto const &_node : _nodes)
220 {
221 auto const &node = _node.second;
222 if (visitedNodesSet.find(node->id()) != visitedNodesSet.end())
223 continue;
224 auto model = node->nodeDataModel();
225 if (areNodeInputsVisitedBefore(*node, *model))
226 {
227 visitor(model);
228 visitedNodesSet.insert(node->id());
229 }
230 }
231 }

254std::vector<Node *> FlowScene::allNodes() const
255{
256 std::vector<Node *> nodes;
257 std::transform(_nodes.begin(), _nodes.end(), std::back_inserter(nodes),
258 [](std::pair<QUuid const, std::unique_ptr<Node>> const &p) { return p.second.get(); });
259 return nodes;
260}
261std::vector<Node *> FlowScene::selectedNodes() const
262{
263 QList<QGraphicsItem *> graphicsItems = selectedItems();
264 std::vector<Node *> ret;
265 ret.reserve(graphicsItems.size());
266 for (QGraphicsItem *item : graphicsItems)
267 {
268 auto ngo = qgraphicsitem_cast<NodeGraphicsObject *>(item);
269 if (ngo != nullptr)
270 {
271 ret.push_back(&ngo->node());
272 }
273 }
274 return ret;
275}
276//------------------------------------------------------------------------------
277void FlowScene::clearScene()
278{
279 // Manual node cleanup. Simply clearing the holding datastructures doesn't
280 // work, the code crashes when
281 // there are both nodes and connections in the scene. (The data propagation
282 // internal logic tries to propagate data through already freed connections.)
283 while (_connections.size() > 0)
284 {
285 deleteConnection(*_connections.begin()->second);
286 }
287 while (_nodes.size() > 0)
288 {
289 removeNode(*_nodes.begin()->second);
290 }
291}
292void FlowScene::save() const
293{
294 QString fileName = QFileDialog::getSaveFileName(nullptr, tr("Open Flow Scene"), QDir::homePath(), tr("Flow Scene Files (*.flow)"));
295 if (!fileName.isEmpty())
296 {
297 if (!fileName.endsWith("flow", Qt::CaseInsensitive))
298 fileName += ".flow";
299 QFile file(fileName);
300 if (file.open(QIODevice::WriteOnly))
301 {
302 file.write(saveToMemory());
303 }
304 }
305}
306void FlowScene::load()
307{
308 QString fileName = QFileDialog::getOpenFileName(nullptr, tr("Open Flow Scene"), QDir::homePath(), tr("Flow Scene Files (*.flow)"));
309 if (!QFileInfo::exists(fileName))
310 return;
311 QFile file(fileName);
312 if (!file.open(QIODevice::ReadOnly))
313 return;
314 QByteArray wholeFile = file.readAll();
315 clearScene();
316 loadFromMemory(wholeFile);
317}
318QByteArray FlowScene::saveToMemory() const
319{
320 QJsonObject sceneJson;
321 QJsonArray nodesJsonArray;
322 for (auto const &pair : _nodes)
323 {
324 auto const &node = pair.second;
325 nodesJsonArray.append(node->save());
326 }
327 sceneJson["nodes"] = nodesJsonArray;
328 QJsonArray connectionJsonArray;
329 for (auto const &pair : _connections)
330 {
331 auto const &connection = pair.second;
332 QJsonObject connectionJson = connection->save();
333 if (!connectionJson.isEmpty())
334 connectionJsonArray.append(connectionJson);
335 }
336 sceneJson["connections"] = connectionJsonArray;
337 QJsonDocument document(sceneJson);
338 return document.toJson();
339}
340void FlowScene::loadFromMemory(const QByteArray &data)
341{
342 QJsonObject const jsonDocument = QJsonDocument::fromJson(data).object();
343 QJsonArray nodesJsonArray = jsonDocument["nodes"].toArray();
344 for (QJsonValueRef node : nodesJsonArray)
345 {
346 restoreNode(node.toObject());
347 }
348 QJsonArray connectionJsonArray = jsonDocument["connections"].toArray();
349 for (QJsonValueRef connection : connectionJsonArray)
350 {
351 restoreConnection(connection.toObject());
352 }
353}
354void FlowScene::setupConnectionSignals(Connection const &c)
355{
356 connect(&c, &Connection::connectionMadeIncomplete, this, &FlowScene::connectionDeleted, Qt::UniqueConnection);
357}
358void FlowScene::sendConnectionCreatedToNodes(Connection const &c)
359{
360 Node *from = c.getNode(PortType::Out);
361 Node *to = c.getNode(PortType::In);
362 Q_ASSERT(from != nullptr);
363 Q_ASSERT(to != nullptr);
364 from->nodeDataModel()->outputConnectionCreated(c);
365 to->nodeDataModel()->inputConnectionCreated(c);
366}
367void FlowScene::sendConnectionDeletedToNodes(Connection const &c)
368{
369 Node *from = c.getNode(PortType::Out);
370 Node *to = c.getNode(PortType::In);
371 Q_ASSERT(from != nullptr);
372 Q_ASSERT(to != nullptr);
373 from->nodeDataModel()->outputConnectionDeleted(c);
374 to->nodeDataModel()->inputConnectionDeleted(c);
375}
376void FlowScene::sceneContextMenuEvent(Node &node, const QPointF &pos)
377{
378 QMenu menu;
379 QAction *embedAction = menu.addAction("Embed");
380 QAction *deembedAction = menu.addAction("Deembed");
381 QGraphicsView *v = node.nodeGraphicsObject().scene()->views().first();
382 QPoint viewP = v->mapFromScene(pos);
383 QAction *selectedAction = menu.exec(v->viewport()->mapToGlobal(viewP));
384 if (selectedAction == embedAction)
385 {
386 node.nodeGraphicsObject().embedQWidget(true);
387 }
388 else if (selectedAction == deembedAction)
389 {
390 node.nodeGraphicsObject().embedQWidget(false);
391 }
392}

394namespace QtNodes
395{
396 Node *locateNodeAt(QPointF scenePoint, FlowScene &scene, QTransform const &viewTransform)
397 {
398 // items under cursor
399 QList<QGraphicsItem *> items = scene.items(scenePoint, Qt::IntersectsItemShape, Qt::DescendingOrder, viewTransform);
400 //// items convertable to NodeGraphicsObject
401 std::vector<QGraphicsItem *> filteredItems;
402 std::copy_if(items.begin(), items.end(), std::back_inserter(filteredItems),
403 [](QGraphicsItem *item) { return (dynamic_cast<NodeGraphicsObject *>(item) != nullptr); });
404 Node *resultNode = nullptr;
405 if (!filteredItems.empty())
406 {
407 QGraphicsItem *graphicsItem = filteredItems.front();
408 auto ngo = dynamic_cast<NodeGraphicsObject *>(graphicsItem);
409 resultNode = &ngo->node();
410 }
411 return resultNode;
412 }
